0 \leq \theta_1, \theta_2 < 360^{\circ}
\theta_1 = 360 \times \frac{y}{60}
\theta_2 = 360 \times \frac{x}{12} + 360\times \frac{y}{60\times 12} = 360(\frac{x}{12} + \frac{y}{60\times 12})
\theta_1 = \theta_2
